songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Aye
Gang
Mr. Bounce out with .44 nigga
Aye
Gang

[Verse]
Real thorough nigga, I ain't ever switched up (nigga)
Couple niggas say I changed, kiss the big bucks (nigga)
I ain't ever changed, I just see you leaching on me (leaching on me)
Got mad, now my niggas started speaking on me (speaking on me)
Aye, it's a shame how they changed, nigga (changed, nigga)
Rocking babies, so I'm staying in my lane witcha (my lane witcha)
Niggas turned they back on me, but you stayed with me (stayed with me)
Only rocking with a few, like my nigga Glizzy (Glizzy)
Niggas speaking on my name when I'm not around (not around)
When I'm around, they think about how they gon' numb me down (they knock me down)
But it's cool, I'm thinking bout how I'm gon' get dough (dough)
By any means, and that's if I gotta cake those (cake those)
You depended on me, well your a man too (you niggas broke)
Get off your ass, and go and show me what that guap do (gang)
Aye, man they shouldn't be so crazy (going crazy)
I don't even know blood, but my mind be going brazy (no blood)
Aye, damn, this shit fucked up
My own man shot at me and missed, so he locked up (bow, bow)
That shit hurts cuz that nigga was my ten hood (ten hood)
Over a bitch, little nigga, why you switched up (switched up)
Aye, it's so crazy how these niggas is (crazy)
Like I'm 50, I be watching out for mini-me (mini-me)
These niggas tryna kill me, just cuz they seen me up (seen me up)
Pay it from my own city, keep that shit a buck (gang)
Say on my life, I'ma try to put this city on (city on)
But if I don't put it on clean, got the throne (throne)
Nigga, snakes in the grass, got my grass cut (grass cut)
And if my tongue cut, bitch, I was really up (really up)
And day to day, I just do it for my nigga valley (ok)
Why the fuck did they have to put my nigga in that Caddy (gang)
Aye, broken hearts, leave a nigga sad (sad)
When you died, it ain't make me sad, it just made me mad (hate it nigga)
What we had, so much shit planned out (planned out)
Skipping safes, we was thinking bout them band routes (chickens)
Niggas speaking on your name, tryna get some fame (fame nigga)
I ain't worried about them niggas, I got perfect aim (bow)
Labels stating, hit me up about some signage shit (signing shit)
It's YBN, big brother, I ain't signing shit  (gang)
You always told me, stay up and don't settle for less (less)
I only listen to you, cuz you told me the best (on my momma)
Bro, that shit so fucked up, why'd you have to die (have to die)
I cried a lot, now a nigga can't even cry (aye)
No, a nigga can't even cry
I know you here, but your spirit somewhere in the sky (sky)
Bro, that shit so fucked up, why'd you have to die (have to die)
I cried a lot, now a nigga can't even cry (aye)
Now, a nigga can't even cry
Aye, now, a nigga can't even cry
I know you here, but your spirit somewhere in the sky (sky)

[Outro]
Man, R.I.P. my nigga Valley, man
Niggas already know how the fuck I'm coming behind, nigga
Nigga, R.I.P. Two Two
Nigga, you know I'm fucking with layover hard
Nigga, shoutout my nigga Nicki, man
SOBxRBE, I'm fucking with their base, for real, nigga
Nigga, stop playing with my nigga name
Before I get up witchu, nigga, that's on my mama, nigga
And Birmingham, where a nigga abduct your motherfucking taco
Bitch
songs.title: Letter 2 Valley Part. 5
